channel.title: Need A Development Team
channel.description:
[center]Hello, and thank you for reading as I sincerely appreciate it! Right now I have been playing and "Trying" to learn how Runescape Private Server's work. But recently I have found a server that my friend plays and noticed it needed some help, since I have a 1 year experience in Java Programming and have never actually applied my java skills to working with a Rsps...I decided to learn.
So that's where this development comes in! I will need a decent development team of atleast 2 more people (if not more) on being patient and helping me out on learning and developing this project. I will be posting my progress and keeping you guys updated on my work as it becomes developed. Since I am new to this type of thing, I would also like suggestions on keeping you guys happy as well as me learning.
Below is the Application field:
Java Skills: What will you be helping with?(Source/Client): Do you have Skype?(If yes Skype Name): Your age: (Just because) Recent Projects/Work: (If any)
That is all for now, I will be posting pictures and what we are doing when we have a team.[/center]
